              <span id="reviewTextContainer126015643" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14936915902799658647">Poignant &amp; poetic story of exile &amp; return, beatifully translated. A must-read for anyone who appreciates lovely prose or is interested in the Palestinian perspective. The tragic part of this story is that it is not the exception; it is the common Palestinian experience. </span>

          </span>
